WEBVTT

00:00:00.719 --> 00:00:02.259
⟨JA⟩? OKAY.

00:00:04.449 --> 00:00:06.601
JETZT LÄUFT DAS BAND VIER

00:00:06.772 --> 00:00:10.873
funem intervyu mit FRAU GENIA Gertslikh.

00:00:11.638 --> 00:00:13.657
yo. dos iz mayn familye.

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:15.817
dos iz mayn man,

00:00:17.511 --> 00:00:19.429
SAMOIL Gertslikh.

00:00:20.194 --> 00:00:21.926
dos iz mayn shnur,

00:00:23.367 --> 00:00:26.668
LILIANA Gertslikh. dos iz mayn eynikl,

00:00:27.619 --> 00:00:29.368
⟨ELI⟩NA Gertslikh.

00:00:30.032 --> 00:00:31.488
dos iz mayn zun,

00:00:31.488 --> 00:00:33.147
ISAAK Gertslikh.

00:00:33.373 --> 00:00:35.172
er iz geboyrn gevorn

00:00:35.550 --> 00:00:37.586
in eyn un fuftsiktn yor,

00:00:37.862 --> 00:00:39.543
dem zibetn monat,

00:00:39.651 --> 00:00:41.012
in Bershad,

00:00:41.018 --> 00:00:42.784
Vinitser OBLAST',

00:00:43.667 --> 00:00:45.517
v⟨u⟩ dos lebn iz nokh geven

00:00:45.658 --> 00:00:47.002
⟨y-⟩ yidish,

00:00:47.903 --> 00:00:49.517
khotsh m'hot nit getort,

00:00:49.675 --> 00:00:51.997
nor mir hobn im gemakht far a yidn,

00:00:52.645 --> 00:00:56.852
vi azoy got hot gebotn, vi azoy es hot gedarft zayn. m'hot im geyidisht.

00:00:56.852 --> 00:00:57.920
s'iz geven

00:00:58.669 --> 00:01:00.854
azoy, vayl mayn foter hot gezogt,

00:01:00.854 --> 00:01:05.396
az bay im in der mishpokhe, bay im in der SEM'YA, ⟨,⟩ darf nor zikh firn yidish.

00:01:08.018 --> 00:01:08.670
UNK.

00:01:09.030 --> 00:01:11.989
dos iz di tokhter mayne, ⟨STELLA⟩.

00:01:11.989 --> 00:01:14.357
zi iz shoyn geboyrn gevorn in Samber

00:01:14.751 --> 00:01:16.533
in nayn un fuftsiktn yor,

00:01:17.063 --> 00:01:19.740
nor a nomen hot men ir gegibn in Bershad,

00:01:20.269 --> 00:01:21.444
in shil,

00:01:21.568 --> 00:01:23.257
azoy vi m'hot gedarft.

00:01:23.257 --> 00:01:24.904
dos hobn mayne eltern geton.

00:01:28.403 --> 00:01:29.662
VOT.

00:01:30.917 --> 00:01:32.796
KHOCHESH' CHTO-TO SKAZAT'?

00:01:34.542 --> 00:01:38.154
nu, CHTO KAZHDYY GOD TY EKHAL...

00:02:06.573 --> 00:02:07.925
nu, ⟨red⟩.

00:02:32.567 --> 00:02:34.835
vu di bist geboyrn gevorn.

00:02:40.695 --> 00:02:43.154
vi azoy du bist geblibn eyner.

00:03:05.788 --> 00:03:07.680
un oyf der pensye.

00:03:21.381 --> 00:03:23.585
un der zun iz gekumen ater tsu,

00:03:24.418 --> 00:03:26.302
hobn mir ale...

00:04:22.654 --> 00:04:23.783
UNK.

00:04:40.727 --> 00:04:42.189
-b ikh a aynden-...

00:04:42.702 --> 00:04:44.569
dos hob ikh a ayndenk

00:04:44.659 --> 00:04:49.529
fun undzer, d⟨i⟩ shtub, vos iz undz geblibn

00:04:49.570 --> 00:04:51.724
nokh der milkhome, nokhn krig.

00:04:53.063 --> 00:04:54.964
dos iz di tsvey lefl

00:04:55.425 --> 00:04:59.183
vos, mit di tsvey gopl, un dos kishele,

00:04:59.644 --> 00:05:02.625
vos iz mir geblibn a ayndenk fun mayn heym.

00:05:03.390 --> 00:05:05.402
mer hob ikh gornit.

00:05:07.221 --> 00:05:08.632
ven mir hobn zikh,

00:05:08.908 --> 00:05:10.235
nokhn krig,

00:05:11.693 --> 00:05:18.521
iz ot dos farblibn. un ven ikh hob khasene gehat hot di mame gegibn mir. hot gezogt, "na. dos halt a ayndenk;

00:05:19.978 --> 00:05:22.672
vifl du vest lebn, zolstu undz dermonen."

00:05:23.067 --> 00:05:25.474
vayl mer hobn zey nit gehat mir vos tsu gibn.

00:05:30.340 --> 00:05:32.511
VSЁ. dos iz mayn babe,

00:05:33.293 --> 00:05:34.150
Libe.

00:05:34.150 --> 00:05:36.729
dos iz der m- mayn muter's muter.

00:05:38.457 --> 00:05:40.813
zi iz geven shtark a frume yidene.

00:05:40.853 --> 00:05:43.254
zi iz geven di eltste in shtetl.

00:05:43.254 --> 00:05:45.757
zi hot opgelebt hundert mit zibn yor.

00:05:46.405 --> 00:05:53.588
far ir gants lebn fleg zi nor mitsves. zi hot gevust vu ⟨s⟩'iz do kranke mentshn, me darf hilf. zi hot gevust vu oreme.

00:05:53.779 --> 00:05:58.487
oyb s'iz geven oreme, vos zey hobn nisht gevolt nemen, zey hobn zikh she- geshemt,

00:05:58.487 --> 00:06:04.084
fleg zi kumen un zogn az "m'hot aykh ibergegibn ayere eygene, ⟨hobn⟩ fun dort, un dort ibergegibn aykh hilf."

00:06:04.866 --> 00:06:06.969
abi fargringern dos lebn.

00:06:08.224 --> 00:06:13.500
un zi hot shtendik moyre gehat nor, az me zol zi nit firn oyf keyn vegele az zi vet shtarbn.

00:06:13.624 --> 00:06:15.862
geshtorbn iz zi vi a frume yidene,

00:06:16.678 --> 00:06:19.203
 fraytik far likht bentshn,

00:06:19.294 --> 00:06:22.573
nor gebahaltn hot men zi zuntik, derfar vos

00:06:22.573 --> 00:06:27.438
⟨s'i-⟩ biz mir zenen gekumen, i- biz ikh bin gekumen tsu forn tsu der levaye...

00:06:28.896 --> 00:06:37.226
⟨un⟩ s'iz geven a shreklekher shney mit a frost, nor m'hot zi getrogn biz in heylikn ort arayn. biz in, grub hot men zi getrogn,

00:06:37.553 --> 00:06:45.107
un oyf ir, lebn ir, bay ir tsukopns zenen geshtanen hunderter likht. dos gantse shtetl iz gekumen PROVOZHAen di bobe Libe.

00:06:46.682 --> 00:06:48.650
azelekhe mentshn vi zi

00:06:48.927 --> 00:06:50.729
zenen merer nisht geven.

00:06:50.729 --> 00:06:55.214
un zi fleg undz shtendik nor dertseyln vos s'iz geven a mol, ⟨,⟩ funem Bal-Shem,

00:06:55.407 --> 00:07:03.028
un far vos me darf moyre hobn, vos me meg un vos me tor nit. zi hot undz gelernt moyde. zi hot undz gelernt shabes oyf der nakht got fun Avrom.

00:07:03.372 --> 00:07:06.437
un mir zenen geven shtark fargleybt in ir.

00:07:07.472 --> 00:07:08.175
UNK

00:07:08.198 --> 00:07:11.651
zi iz geven shtark a reyne, yidene.

00:07:11.860 --> 00:07:16.224
⟨i⟩n dem, tog vos zi hot gedarft shtarbn hot zi gefilt az zi shtarbt.

00:07:16.281 --> 00:07:18.975
dos iz geven erev khanuke.

00:07:19.588 --> 00:07:22.167
 hot zi mayn muter avekgeshikt fun der shtub,

00:07:22.167 --> 00:07:25.928
un hot gezogt, "gey, vestu koyfn di eyniklekh, mayne ureyniklekh,

00:07:25.950 --> 00:07:27.187
PODARKes,

00:07:27.187 --> 00:07:29.471
un tsu mir loz araynkumen di shkheyne."

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:32.762
di shkheyne iz nor gekumen, un zi hot ⟨nor⟩ gegibn gelt.

00:07:33.308 --> 00:07:39.326
un mayn muter hot gezen az zi shtarbt. zogt zi, "mame, zog mir, ver se kumt dir, bay vemen se kumt dir gelt."

00:07:39.332 --> 00:07:41.199
vayl zi fleg tseteyln.

00:07:41.661 --> 00:07:45.817
hot zi gezogt, "ver s'vet hobn got in harts vet aleyn opgibn,

00:07:45.817 --> 00:07:47.443
un ver se hot nit,

00:07:47.584 --> 00:07:49.639
iz loz dos ot ⟨ot⟩ azoy zayn."

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:54.547
iz nor eyn shkheyne hot opgegibn etlekhe un fertsik rubl,

00:07:55.313 --> 00:07:59.323
hot mayn muter nokh derleygt un hot mir gekoyft a fingerl a PAMYAT',

00:07:59.835 --> 00:08:02.141
az ikh zol hobn a ayndenk fun der baben.

00:08:03.818 --> 00:08:04.723
o!

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:10.556
 zi hot gehat a shtark a shver lebn, vayl zi iz geblibn eyne aleyn

00:08:10.556 --> 00:08:14.471
fun zeks un tsvontsik yor, a almone mit,

00:08:14.471 --> 00:08:17.565
mayn muter iz nokh geven bay ir in boykh.

00:08:17.689 --> 00:08:19.336
der zeyde iz geshtorbn

00:08:19.495 --> 00:08:21.328
fun a SIMBIRSKe YAZVe.

00:08:21.773 --> 00:08:27.616
hot zi zikh shtark gemutshet. zi fleg bakn broyt un makhn konfetn un, ⟨f-⟩

00:08:27.616 --> 00:08:28.786
 shpinen,

00:08:28.928 --> 00:08:30.486
un, ⟨f-⟩

00:08:30.486 --> 00:08:36.161
⟨, ⟩ POLOTNO makhn. alesding hot zi geton, az zi zol kenen ire kinder helfn.

00:08:37.551 --> 00:08:44.649
un hot zikh fardint oyfn lebn. un vos zi fleg helf-, ton, hot, iz ⟨g- got⟩, got mit ir, un ⟨se⟩ fleg ⟨ir z-⟩ geyn mit der hant.

00:08:44.706 --> 00:08:49.504
oyb hot zi gebakn broyt oyf farkoyfn, iz ir broyt geven dos shenste; me fleg shteyn in otshered.

00:08:49.504 --> 00:08:53.441
oyb zi hot gemakht konfetn, iz ire konfetn zenen geven di shenste;

00:08:53.650 --> 00:08:57.626
me fleg shteyn in otshered tsun ir. oyb zi fleg bakn PECHEN'E,

00:08:57.649 --> 00:08:59.342
iz ir PECHEN'E geven...

00:08:59.342 --> 00:09:01.423
zi iz geven a groyse baleboste.

00:09:02.307 --> 00:09:04.616
UNK un iz geven shtark a gute ⟨bobe⟩.

00:09:09.664 --> 00:09:11.328
dos iz mayn muter.

00:09:12.617 --> 00:09:15.800
do iz zi oyf der fotografye alt geven zibetsik yor.

00:09:16.735 --> 00:09:18.990
zi hot zikh fotografirt oyfn pasport.

00:09:18.990 --> 00:09:19.951
zi hot oykhet

00:09:20.481 --> 00:09:22.449
lib gehat mitsves tsu ton.

00:09:22.776 --> 00:09:25.065
zi iz geven shtark a getraye muter.

00:09:29.408 --> 00:09:31.444
az ikh bin avekgeforn fun der heym,

00:09:33.829 --> 00:09:36.995
hob ikh zey shtark gefelt oyf di eltere yorn,

00:09:37.221 --> 00:09:39.459
vayl ikh fleg zey helfn

00:09:40.005 --> 00:09:41.231
mit alemen.

00:09:42.621 --> 00:09:44.420
nu, vos ken ikh nokh zogn?

00:09:45.051 --> 00:09:47.233
in Bershad hot men zi gekent

00:09:47.233 --> 00:09:50.549
far a frume yidene vos zi hot lib gehat mitsves tsu ton,

00:09:50.549 --> 00:09:52.369
azoy vi di muter ire.

00:09:53.914 --> 00:09:55.298
VSЁ.

00:10:02.618 --> 00:10:05.700
dos iz mayn foter, Avreml ⟨Trenker⟩.

00:10:05.993 --> 00:10:08.282
im hot gekent di gantse shtetl.

00:10:08.389 --> 00:10:10.931
ver s'hot gedarft hobn holts oyfn vinter,

00:10:11.308 --> 00:10:13.074
ver s'hot gedarft epes...

00:10:15.055 --> 00:10:19.268
er hot a shtark a shver lebn oykhet gehat. er iz geblibn yung a yosem.

00:10:19.763 --> 00:10:21.174
er hot gearbet

00:10:22.918 --> 00:10:24.346
in a ulinye

00:10:24.437 --> 00:10:25.933
bay a balebos.

00:10:26.091 --> 00:10:30.793
dernokh hot er gearbet nokh a PRO- PRIKAZCHIK, bizkele m'hot RASKURKAL-, -KULIVet

00:10:31.069 --> 00:10:34.640
di, vos zey hobn gehat eygene ulinyes, eygene miln.

00:10:35.372 --> 00:10:38.285
dernokh fleg er arbetn oyf alerley arbetn.

00:10:41.413 --> 00:10:45.221
di OSNOVNOY arbet iz bay im geven vos er fleg forn in vald arayn

00:10:45.261 --> 00:10:47.044
un aroysfirn holts.

00:10:48.906 --> 00:10:51.043
un az di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn...

00:10:51.454 --> 00:10:55.666
nu, hob ikh gezogt, hot men im farnemen keyn Nikolayever kontslager,

00:10:55.993 --> 00:10:58.417
un fun dortn iz er gekumen a kranker.

00:10:58.677 --> 00:11:00.805
er hot astme gehat,

00:11:01.123 --> 00:11:04.864
nor der guter UKHOD vos er hot gehat bay mayn muter,

00:11:05.595 --> 00:11:08.306
hot er gekent lebn biz dray un nayntsik yor.

00:11:13.223 --> 00:11:14.246
aha.

00:11:15.906 --> 00:11:17.554
in nayntsiktn yor

00:11:17.779 --> 00:11:20.422
hot men fotografirt undzer shtetl,

00:11:21.103 --> 00:11:23.479
ven di yidn hobn ongehoybn aroystsuforn:

00:11:23.479 --> 00:11:25.181
di yidishe shil...

00:11:25.181 --> 00:11:28.938
vayl se fleg zayn bay undz nokh a yidishe PEREDACHe, "YAKHAD,"

00:11:28.938 --> 00:11:31.880
fun Kiev. fleg men kumen un fotografirn.

00:11:32.747 --> 00:11:35.643
mir zenen gekumen atin tsu forn tsu zey.

00:11:36.544 --> 00:11:38.563
hot mayn muter zikh farklogt,

00:11:38.687 --> 00:11:41.128
az der foter iz geven in shil

00:11:41.455 --> 00:11:49.110
un m'hot im fotografirt. "oyf vos t⟨oy⟩g es im?" m'hot shtark moyre gehat, vayl me fleg far azelekhe zakhn nokh, sudyen, arestirn.

00:11:50.263 --> 00:11:57.142
"tsu vos ⟨toyg im⟩ oyf di eltere yorn? un me zol kholile no⟨kh⟩ di kinder nit, rufn far derfar." hobn mir zikh oysgelakht fun zey,

00:11:57.638 --> 00:11:59.373
un mir hobn gezogt az di shil

00:11:59.373 --> 00:12:01.558
iz in FINOTDEL oyfn UCHЁТ;

00:12:01.558 --> 00:12:06.103
s'iz do tsvontsik mentshn, vos zey geyen un m'hot zey farregistrirt, me tsolt.

00:12:06.413 --> 00:12:08.196
"ir darft nit PEREZHIVAen."

00:12:08.370 --> 00:12:09.123
nu,

00:12:09.467 --> 00:12:11.362
un azoy iz dos shoyn geven.

00:12:11.362 --> 00:12:13.427
mit dem hobn mir ⟨U⟩SPOKOet di mame.

00:12:14.547 --> 00:12:17.629
un mir hobn nisht gevust tsulib vos m'hot fotografirt.

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:22.719
ven mir hobn avekgeshtelt, krik mit

00:12:22.719 --> 00:12:27.990
dray, fir khadoshim hobn mir avekgeshtelt atin, a RUSSKe antene, a rusishe.

00:12:28.789 --> 00:12:31.196
un mir hobn oyf der nakht VKLYUCHAet.

00:12:31.236 --> 00:12:32.833
mir gibn a kuk,

00:12:33.565 --> 00:12:36.916
⟨zogt⟩, vi tsvey meydelekh zenen geshtanen

00:12:37.699 --> 00:12:40.983
un m'hot dertseylt far vos me bakt matses,

00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:43.886
far vos di yidn praven peysekh azoy.

00:12:44.787 --> 00:12:47.093
VSЁ, der tekst hot zikh geendikt,

00:12:47.605 --> 00:12:49.766
un dernokh dem hot men gevizn,

00:12:49.815 --> 00:12:52.964
⟨⟩, dos kleyne shtetele Bershad.

00:12:53.055 --> 00:12:55.648
nu, dos iz geven oyf rusish, altsding.

00:12:57.477 --> 00:12:59.411
dos hot mayn man derzen.

00:12:59.974 --> 00:13:00.980
zogt er,

00:13:01.138 --> 00:13:02.299
"gib a kuk!

00:13:02.299 --> 00:13:04.206
Bershad vet men bald vayzn."

00:13:04.206 --> 00:13:07.058
er hot bald gezen di yidishe gasn,

00:13:07.058 --> 00:13:10.920
azoy vi di yidn pakeven di kestlekh oyf aroystsuforn,

00:13:12.428 --> 00:13:19.374
di yidishe shil. zogt er, "ot iz er, Genye, gib a kuk, di yidishe shil!" un azoy hot mayn foter, ibern gantsn ekran,

00:13:19.431 --> 00:13:20.736
hot men im gevizn,

00:13:20.736 --> 00:13:22.749
azoy vi er geyt aroys fun der shil,

00:13:24.527 --> 00:13:26.507
dernokh dem nokh fir yidn.

00:13:26.507 --> 00:13:29.348
nor dem oyfdernakht kent ir zikh forshteln.

00:13:30.687 --> 00:13:34.255
dos iz geven, in nayntsiktn yor hot men fotografirt,

00:13:34.255 --> 00:13:37.076
un Rusland hot gevizn dem film

00:13:37.521 --> 00:13:39.124
VOT ersht itstert.

00:13:39.529 --> 00:13:41.340
dem film hot men gezen

00:13:41.340 --> 00:13:43.725
in, IZRAIL' oykhet.

00:13:44.811 --> 00:13:50.019
⟨m'hot⟩ mir geklungen un m'hot gebetn, az me vet, ⟨ikh⟩ zol aroysshikn di,

00:13:50.211 --> 00:13:51.954
 KASSETe,

00:13:51.954 --> 00:13:56.434
az zey zoln kenen nokh a mol un nokh a mol zen, vayl shtark a sakh Bershader

00:13:56.434 --> 00:13:58.254
in di gasn un ales.

00:13:58.429 --> 00:14:04.073
nu, mir hobn gebetn az oyb me vet zayn, zol men undz demlt onklingen, az mir zoln kenen zikh oykhet

00:14:04.073 --> 00:14:04.818
mit dem...

00:14:05.061 --> 00:14:06.861
mayn foter hot opgelebt

00:14:06.861 --> 00:14:08.345
dray un nayntsik yor.

00:14:08.706 --> 00:14:10.556
er iz geshtorbn nokh der muter

00:14:11.423 --> 00:14:12.508
in IZRAIL'.

00:14:12.508 --> 00:14:17.508
di muter oykhet in IZRAIL', nor di muter iz geven alt nayntsik un der foter dray un nayntsik.

00:14:21.582 --> 00:14:23.601
dos iz vayter mayn muter,

00:14:23.742 --> 00:14:26.255
lebn undzer shtub, oyf undzer gas,

00:14:26.255 --> 00:14:28.578
oyf d- vu mir hobn gevoynt dortn,

00:14:29.040 --> 00:14:30.603
mit nokh a shokhn,

00:14:31.116 --> 00:14:32.443
bay zayn tishl.

00:14:33.090 --> 00:14:36.015
dos iz shoyn farn avekforn keyn IZRAIL'

00:14:36.015 --> 00:14:38.028
dos ⟨ge-⟩ bild gemakht gevorn,

00:14:39.267 --> 00:14:40.172
in

00:14:41.477 --> 00:14:44.646
tsvey, oder in tsvey un draysi- nayn un,

00:14:44.646 --> 00:14:46.500
tsvey un nayntsiktn

00:14:47.198 --> 00:14:48.069
yor.

00:14:53.037 --> 00:14:55.933
dos bild iz fun mayn DVOYURODNe shvester.

00:14:56.057 --> 00:14:58.565
dos iz gemakht gevorn in fertsiktn yor.

00:15:00.647 --> 00:15:02.413
dos iz ⟨Buzi Halevitsh⟩.

00:15:03.128 --> 00:15:07.087
ir familye shteyt dortn oyf der obelisk in Bershad.

00:15:07.735 --> 00:15:09.399
geharget hot men zi

00:15:09.473 --> 00:15:14.908
in, ende,

00:15:15.008 --> 00:15:16.790
dray un fertsiktn

00:15:17.202 --> 00:15:21.971
oder in onheyb fir un fertsiktn yor, far derinen vos m'hot undz OB-,

00:15:22.045 --> 00:15:23.439
OSVOBODet,

00:15:23.496 --> 00:15:25.245
vi a partizanke.

00:15:27.546 --> 00:15:31.657
shreklekhn toyt hot zi gehat, vayl m'hot geshnitn shtiklekh fun ir.

00:15:32.592 --> 00:15:33.323
VSЁ.

00:15:33.323 --> 00:15:34.770
vos ken ikh nokh...?

00:15:36.591 --> 00:15:38.103
dos iz mayn man,

00:15:38.700 --> 00:15:40.297
oyfn PAROVOZ,

00:15:40.658 --> 00:15:43.520
vu er hot opgearbet... lokomotiv...

00:15:43.712 --> 00:15:45.413
eyn un fertsik yor

00:15:45.413 --> 00:15:47.057
hot er opgearbet.

00:15:47.965 --> 00:15:52.819
er iz oykhet eyner geblibn fun der gantser SEM'YA. m'hot ale oysgeharget

00:15:53.162 --> 00:15:54.455
in VARSHAVe.

00:15:55.710 --> 00:15:57.408
un nokh der milkhome

00:15:58.140 --> 00:16:00.462
hobn mir zikh bagegnt oyf der Ukraine,

00:16:01.583 --> 00:16:04.549
vu mir hobn, voynen biz hayntikn yor,

00:16:04.549 --> 00:16:06.065
biz hayntikn tog.

00:16:09.447 --> 00:16:12.582
-os bild iz mayn, muter's

00:16:12.582 --> 00:16:14.317
DVOYURODNe bruder,

00:16:14.509 --> 00:16:15.510
a kuzin,

00:16:15.510 --> 00:16:17.574
un der eygener bruder, Leyb.

00:16:17.935 --> 00:16:20.814
im hot zi nit gezen keyn eyn un draysik yor,

00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:24.369
vayl m'hot nit getort; m'hot gemakht a grenets

00:16:24.369 --> 00:16:26.653
fun der Ukraine biz Moldavye,

00:16:26.828 --> 00:16:28.391
un m'hot zikh nit gezen.

00:16:28.448 --> 00:16:32.863
er hot gevoynt in Vertyuzhane un zi hot gevoynt in Bershad.

00:16:33.561 --> 00:16:35.777
un ven der krig hot zikh ongehoybn,

00:16:35.777 --> 00:16:38.145
hot er mit zayn SEM'YA, -MEYSTVe

00:16:39.130 --> 00:16:43.832
gebetn zikh az er fort keyn Bershad; er hot gemeynt az dortn vet er zayn geholfn.

00:16:44.007 --> 00:16:47.632
nor m'hot im gezogt az Bershad iz shoyn bombirt.

00:16:47.632 --> 00:16:49.977
iz er avekgeforn mit zayn SEMEYSTVe

00:16:49.977 --> 00:16:51.527
keyn SREDNe Azye.

00:16:51.668 --> 00:16:54.550
un dortn iz, zenen zey ale lebn geblibn.

00:16:54.550 --> 00:16:55.639
un der,

00:16:55.639 --> 00:16:57.078
dem hot men geharget.

00:16:56.287 --> 00:16:58.023
link⟨e⟩?

00:16:57.675 --> 00:16:58.423
yo.

00:16:58.423 --> 00:17:00.960
hot men im geharget in plen

00:17:01.033 --> 00:17:04.030
in, in Pavlograd,

00:17:04.324 --> 00:17:10.252
vayl se zenen gekumen azelekhe mentshn vos zenen oykhet geven mit im in eynem, un m'hot im gebetn, "antloyf."

00:17:10.252 --> 00:17:11.506
hot er moyre gehat

00:17:11.647 --> 00:17:13.176
az me vet im hargenen.

00:17:13.858 --> 00:17:15.669
iz, hot men im dortn geharget,

00:17:15.669 --> 00:17:16.770
di daytshn.

00:17:22.178 --> 00:17:23.556
dos bild

00:17:24.387 --> 00:17:26.862
iz gemakht gevorn shoyn in Samber.

00:17:27.223 --> 00:17:28.533
bin ikh shoyn geven

00:17:29.417 --> 00:17:35.013
dray un draysik oder fir un draysik yor. dos iz oyfn pasport, hot men gedarft zikh fotografirn.

00:17:35.509 --> 00:17:36.508
VSЁ.

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:43.157
dos iz d- dos bild,

00:17:43.157 --> 00:17:45.712
mayn bruder mit zayne eyniklekh

00:17:46.073 --> 00:17:50.134
oyfn rusishn nayem yor bay der yolke in Bershad,

00:17:50.460 --> 00:17:52.209
zenen zey fotografirt.

00:17:52.975 --> 00:17:53.796
VSЁ.

00:17:54.645 --> 00:17:56.883
dos iz mir geblibn a ayndenk fun im.

00:17:59.944 --> 00:18:01.704
dos iz mayn kuzin,

00:18:01.704 --> 00:18:03.515
⟨Dodik Halevitsh⟩.

00:18:03.825 --> 00:18:05.493
er iz eyner geblibn

00:18:05.493 --> 00:18:07.636
fun der SEM'-, fun der SEMEYSTVe.

00:18:07.636 --> 00:18:09.522
dem foter hot men geharget,

00:18:10.170 --> 00:18:12.470
di muter hot men geharget,

00:18:12.470 --> 00:18:17.066
di shvester mit di brider, ale hot men oysgeharget. er iz eyner geblibn,

00:18:17.241 --> 00:18:20.812
vayl er iz geven oykhet in Nikolayevske kontslager,

00:18:20.869 --> 00:18:24.035
un er iz gekumen far derinen vos m'hot undz bafrayt.

00:18:24.649 --> 00:18:26.685
⟨un⟩ derfar iz er lebn geblibn.

00:18:26.758 --> 00:18:29.087
vayter volt men im oykh geven geharget.

00:18:29.123 --> 00:18:29.958
⟨VSЁ⟩.

00:18:29.958 --> 00:18:31.832
yetst voynt er in IZRAIL'.

00:18:37.947 --> 00:18:39.881
dos iz mayn man.

00:18:40.832 --> 00:18:45.433
oyf dem f-, oyf der foto iz im geven finef un draysik yor.

00:18:47.093 --> 00:18:47.931
shoyn.

00:18:49.860 --> 00:18:50.525
⟨DA⟩.

00:18:50.525 --> 00:18:53.178
dos bild iz gemakht gevorn

00:18:53.775 --> 00:18:55.946
in zibn un akhtsiktn yor.

00:18:56.239 --> 00:18:58.443
dos iz di khasene fun mayn zun.

00:18:58.804 --> 00:18:59.931
di shnur,

00:18:59.931 --> 00:19:01.802
un zeyere eydes.

00:19:01.926 --> 00:19:03.354
dos iz ⟨Rome⟩

00:19:03.377 --> 00:19:06.116
⟨Nakhlis⟩, der, zayn khaver,

00:19:06.116 --> 00:19:06.999
un do...

00:19:07.090 --> 00:19:07.877
ha?

00:19:08.271 --> 00:19:09.356
un do

00:19:09.356 --> 00:19:11.454
iz ir khaverte,

00:19:11.477 --> 00:19:13.051
der shnur's.

00:19:13.924 --> 00:19:16.061
do iz mayn tokhter,

00:19:17.417 --> 00:19:18.595
mayn man,

00:19:18.595 --> 00:19:19.432
ikh,

00:19:19.415 --> 00:19:20.690
hintn links?

00:19:20.556 --> 00:19:27.261
un der shnur's foter, der mekhutn undzerer, mit der mekhuteneste, mit zeyer zun,

00:19:27.261 --> 00:19:28.160
IGOR'.

00:19:29.601 --> 00:19:30.388
VSЁ.

00:19:31.963 --> 00:19:34.100
oyf dem bild, dos iz mayn zun,

00:19:34.343 --> 00:19:35.991
ven er hot gedint

00:19:36.351 --> 00:19:38.100
in der KRASNe armye.

00:19:38.730 --> 00:19:44.242
UNK do UNK ⟨alt⟩ geven nayntsn yor. gedint hot er in Moldavye, in ⟨Bendere⟩.

00:19:46.155 --> 00:19:47.161
VSЁ.

00:19:52.020 --> 00:19:53.333
do iz mayn tokhter,

00:19:53.333 --> 00:19:54.435
⟨STELLA⟩.

00:19:56.230 --> 00:19:58.181
gemakht gevorn dos bild

00:19:58.255 --> 00:20:00.808
ven ir iz geven tsvey un tsv⟨a⟩ntsik yor,

00:20:00.808 --> 00:20:01.860
in L'VOV.

00:20:04.397 --> 00:20:06.752
voynt zi dortn biz hayntikn tog

00:20:06.752 --> 00:20:09.909
un vart di RAZRESHENIE oyf tsu kumen ater.

00:20:12.548 --> 00:20:17.503
dos bild iz gemakht gevorn in dray un nayntsiktn yor in IZRAIL',

00:20:17.509 --> 00:20:20.928
ven ikh bin gekumen tsu, in gest tsu mayne eltern.

00:20:22.234 --> 00:20:24.996
dos iz ale undzer mishpokhe.

00:20:26.301 --> 00:20:28.117
do iz mayn foter

00:20:28.275 --> 00:20:29.585
mit der muter,

00:20:31.380 --> 00:20:33.770
di shvegerin, mayn bruder's froy,

00:20:34.620 --> 00:20:36.284
mit ire eyniklekh.

00:20:36.426 --> 00:20:40.245
dos iz a DVOYURODNe bruder, a kuzin, mit zayn froy,

00:20:40.245 --> 00:20:41.702
un mayn tokhter.

00:20:46.450 --> 00:20:49.493
dos bild iz oykh gemakht gevorn in E-

00:20:49.493 --> 00:20:50.764
Erets-Yisroel

00:20:50.787 --> 00:20:52.682
in dray un nayntsiktn yor,

00:20:52.682 --> 00:20:54.156
ven ikh bin gekumen.

00:20:54.583 --> 00:20:58.942
dos iz zeyer ort vu ⟨zey zene-⟩ flegn zitsn, der foter mit der muter,

00:20:58.942 --> 00:21:02.356
un ver se fleg durkhgeyn fun bakente hobn zikh opgeshtelt.

00:21:03.122 --> 00:21:06.929
zey hobn gevoynt oyf der gas ⟨Broynde⟩, DEV- nayn

00:21:07.206 --> 00:21:08.820
bay a balebos

00:21:09.282 --> 00:21:12.216
vos er hot zey opgeteylt a kleyn shtikl ort,

00:21:12.216 --> 00:21:14.624
nor vos zey hobn gehat zikh vu oystsudreyen.

00:21:15.255 --> 00:21:16.413
 shreklekh!

00:21:17.382 --> 00:21:18.945
un farn toyt

00:21:19.322 --> 00:21:21.695
hot er zikh barekhnt, vayl zayn froy

00:21:21.904 --> 00:21:25.804
iz oykhet geshtorbn a yor f- krik mit, ⟨v- eyder⟩ zey.

00:21:25.804 --> 00:21:27.568
hot zi im shtark gebetn,

00:21:27.709 --> 00:21:28.749
"Meyer,

00:21:29.127 --> 00:21:33.778
efn oyf di alte layt nokh a KOMNATkele; lomen zikh hobn vu oystsudreyen."

00:21:34.729 --> 00:21:40.460
hot er oyfgeefnt. UNK gehaltn di tsavoe fun zayn froy.

00:21:40.585 --> 00:21:46.851
